{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/2015/2015-03-04-kk/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Fan's life"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"d9f75510-b6f6-5ba8-aec0-4e6aa1951a2d","excerpt":"简介 功夫小子是一款多人格斗竞技游戏，无成长，游戏中可切换武器，强调武器平衡及个人技术\n\n 开发：盛大成都研发 运营：盛大上海（后转入成都锦天） 上线时间：2007 年 运营状态：alive…","html":"<h2>简介</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"http://kk.8yx.com/\">功夫小子</a>是一款多人格斗竞技游戏，无成长，游戏中可切换武器，强调武器平衡及个人技术\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 78.48101265822784%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"大厅\"\n        title=\"大厅\"\n        src=\"/static/75cd9e923be0ca0147cda7ff95cbeaf1/828fb/lobby.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/75cd9e923be0ca0147cda7ff95cbeaf1/ff44c/lobby.jpg 158w,\n/static/75cd9e923be0ca0147cda7ff95cbeaf1/a6688/lobby.jpg 315w,\n/static/75cd9e923be0ca0147cda7ff95cbeaf1/828fb/lobby.jpg 630w,\n/static/75cd9e923be0ca0147cda7ff95cbeaf1/31be4/lobby.jpg 806w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span>\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 44.93670886075949%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"战斗\"\n        title=\"战斗\"\n        src=\"/static/8474120cf10a40d79c0cb5520f7e6f5d/828fb/battle.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/8474120cf10a40d79c0cb5520f7e6f5d/ff44c/battle.jpg 158w,\n/static/8474120cf10a40d79c0cb5520f7e6f5d/a6688/battle.jpg 315w,\n/static/8474120cf10a40d79c0cb5520f7e6f5d/828fb/battle.jpg 630w,\n/static/8474120cf10a40d79c0cb5520f7e6f5d/0ede0/battle.jpg 945w,\n/static/8474120cf10a40d79c0cb5520f7e6f5d/50055/battle.jpg 1012w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></li>\n<li>开发：盛大成都研发</li>\n<li>运营：盛大上海（后转入成都锦天）</li>\n<li>上线时间：2007 年</li>\n<li>运营状态：alive</li>\n<li>盈利模式：免费卖道具的方式，主营是武器。由于一开始就卖了永久的武器，所以后来都不做限时武器了，全部是永久的。\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 601px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/0fca3f0fb9a3620752aa62f8b3cb6f8d/5ed3f/weapon.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 66.45569620253164%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"武器\"\n        title=\"武器\"\n        src=\"/static/0fca3f0fb9a3620752aa62f8b3cb6f8d/5ed3f/weapon.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/0fca3f0fb9a3620752aa62f8b3cb6f8d/ff44c/weapon.jpg 158w,\n/static/0fca3f0fb9a3620752aa62f8b3cb6f8d/a6688/weapon.jpg 315w,\n/static/0fca3f0fb9a3620752aa62f8b3cb6f8d/5ed3f/weapon.jpg 601w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 601px) 100vw, 601px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></li>\n<li>最高时做到过盛大全公司收入前十</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>盛大特色</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>彩虹帮助：盛大要求所有游戏都必须在游戏内置彩虹帮助，让玩家可以直接联系查询常见问题以及联系客服\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 325px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/d0a6c52265dc3b02047c10a419d73907/ff46a/help.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 34.810126582278485%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"帮助\"\n        title=\"帮助\"\n        src=\"/static/d0a6c52265dc3b02047c10a419d73907/ff46a/help.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/d0a6c52265dc3b02047c10a419d73907/c26ae/help.png 158w,\n/static/d0a6c52265dc3b02047c10a419d73907/6bdcf/help.png 315w,\n/static/d0a6c52265dc3b02047c10a419d73907/ff46a/help.png 325w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 325px) 100vw, 325px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></li>\n<li>快捷消费：要求所有游戏必须给玩家提供冲动消费的方式，有点儿类似亚马逊的一键下单。截图中最下面一行的道具都是直接花人民币的，都是一键使用。\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/8474120cf10a40d79c0cb5520f7e6f5d/50055/battle.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 44.93670886075949%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"战斗\"\n        title=\"战斗\"\n        src=\"/static/8474120cf10a40d79c0cb5520f7e6f5d/828fb/battle.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/8474120cf10a40d79c0cb5520f7e6f5d/ff44c/battle.jpg 158w,\n/static/8474120cf10a40d79c0cb5520f7e6f5d/a6688/battle.jpg 315w,\n/static/8474120cf10a40d79c0cb5520f7e6f5d/828fb/battle.jpg 630w,\n/static/8474120cf10a40d79c0cb5520f7e6f5d/0ede0/battle.jpg 945w,\n/static/8474120cf10a40d79c0cb5520f7e6f5d/50055/battle.jpg 1012w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></li>\n<li>各种喇叭：这是从泡泡堂继承的有效的收入手段。小喇叭主要在聊天位置发所有玩家可见消息，大喇叭会在聊天位置发所有玩家可见消息，心情喇叭会在公告栏的位置发消息。玩家很买账，这是泡泡堂的主要收入来源。基本上所有的盛大游戏都有这个：\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/8950d03bd1d6189ff091012d12807192/a6d32/chat.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 70.88607594936708%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"聊天\"\n        title=\"聊天\"\n        src=\"/static/8950d03bd1d6189ff091012d12807192/828fb/chat.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/8950d03bd1d6189ff091012d12807192/ff44c/chat.jpg 158w,\n/static/8950d03bd1d6189ff091012d12807192/a6688/chat.jpg 315w,\n/static/8950d03bd1d6189ff091012d12807192/828fb/chat.jpg 630w,\n/static/8950d03bd1d6189ff091012d12807192/a6d32/chat.jpg 652w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span>\n下半部黄的是大喇叭，中间是心情喇叭。</li>\n<li>论坛：所有游戏都有的论坛，论坛入口都很好记形如：<a href=\"http://bbs.8yx.com/\">http://bbs.8yx.com</a>\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 49.36708860759494%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"论坛\"\n        title=\"论坛\"\n        src=\"/static/f595f8afb9c7e1f7cf8dd51eaab2c6ac/f058b/bbs.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/f595f8afb9c7e1f7cf8dd51eaab2c6ac/c26ae/bbs.png 158w,\n/static/f595f8afb9c7e1f7cf8dd51eaab2c6ac/6bdcf/bbs.png 315w,\n/static/f595f8afb9c7e1f7cf8dd51eaab2c6ac/f058b/bbs.png 630w,\n/static/f595f8afb9c7e1f7cf8dd51eaab2c6ac/146da/bbs.png 943w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></li>\n<li>客服：盛大的客服很早就转移到成都来了，主要通过论坛和电话和玩家沟通。邮件的方式倒是非常少。客服是三班倒，保证任何时刻都有人回答论坛的问题以及接听玩家电话。</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>运营方式</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>周末活动：每周末都会做提升在线的活动\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/b6ca4f2e71e2c67f14bdedf1fa8409d7/cab8c/active.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 104.43037974683544%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"活动\"\n        title=\"活动\"\n        src=\"/static/b6ca4f2e71e2c67f14bdedf1fa8409d7/f058b/active.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/b6ca4f2e71e2c67f14bdedf1fa8409d7/c26ae/active.png 158w,\n/static/b6ca4f2e71e2c67f14bdedf1fa8409d7/6bdcf/active.png 315w,\n/static/b6ca4f2e71e2c67f14bdedf1fa8409d7/f058b/active.png 630w,\n/static/b6ca4f2e71e2c67f14bdedf1fa8409d7/cab8c/active.png 744w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></li>\n<li>节日活动：不放过任何节日，除了情人节、圣诞节、元旦、春节、国庆、五一，还有七夕、端午、感恩节、教师节等，甚至还有双十一\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/49f8a8251135c80ab37aaf25c46e212e/b6e34/holiday.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 83.54430379746836%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"节日\"\n        title=\"节日\"\n        src=\"/static/49f8a8251135c80ab37aaf25c46e212e/f058b/holiday.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/49f8a8251135c80ab37aaf25c46e212e/c26ae/holiday.png 158w,\n/static/49f8a8251135c80ab37aaf25c46e212e/6bdcf/holiday.png 315w,\n/static/49f8a8251135c80ab37aaf25c46e212e/f058b/holiday.png 630w,\n/static/49f8a8251135c80ab37aaf25c46e212e/40601/holiday.png 945w,\n/static/49f8a8251135c80ab37aaf25c46e212e/b6e34/holiday.png 1103w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></li>\n<li>武馆争霸：定期举办各个武馆（公会）之间的比赛</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>其他</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>盛大的运营有一定技术水平，功夫小子的数据分析工具和商城上下架工具都是运营自己写的。</li>\n<li>运营主管要求所有运营每天必须要打几个小时游戏，因此运营基本都是 KK 的玩家，同时也对游戏有很深的了解。</li>\n<li>由于研发在成都、运营在上海，又是属于盛大这个大公司，实际上研发对玩家的响应速度并不快。压力也不大。</li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"title":"功夫小子运营","date":"March 04, 2015","description":null}},"previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/2014/2014-03-27-pixar/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Pixar的哲学和方法"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/2016/2016-09-19-linux/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Linux开发经验教训——来自《Linux 内核开发报告2016版》"}}},"pageContext":{"id":"d9f75510-b6f6-5ba8-aec0-4e6aa1951a2d","previousPostId":"503c8c98-52a6-59ea-99fd-38aa993d6aa0","nextPostId":"fa8c38a8-af11-5d56-95e2-69ae9e901294"}},"staticQueryHashes":["2841359383","916993862"]}